<li id="cite_note-70"><b><a href="#cite_ref-70" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.1911encyclopedia.org/Breaking_on_the_wheel" class="external text" title="http://www.1911encyclopedia.org/Breaking_on_the_wheel" rel="nofollow">Breaking on the wheel - LoveToKnow 1911</a></li>
</ol>
